{"id": 1632, "genre": 1001, "title": "在当下，你对于“个人空间”的定义是什么？", "description": "这是我自己的空间，别来打扰我。（题图来自：林小妖）", "record_count": 3864, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170425171927OeosSz6j1xW2Brlt.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-04-26T03:00:59Z", "options": [{"id": 196864, "content": "一个人思想的独处", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1015401}, {"id": 197120, "content": "关机！", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 170463}, {"id": 197376, "content": "一个人在喜欢的地方，做喜欢的事", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1016513}, {"id": 197632, "content": "小号", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 766293}, {"id": 199424, "content": "关上门，上厕所的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1021023}, {"id": 196865, "content": "微信的聊天记录", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1013082}, {"id": 197121, "content": "有一个可以放自己东西的地方", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 821461}, {"id": 197377, "content": "一个人在喜欢的地方，做喜欢的事", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1016513}, {"id": 199425, "content": "关上门，上厕所的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1021023}, {"id": 196866, "content": "我也不喜欢我在看电脑看手机或学习的时候被人盯着。。或别人突然伸个头过来问你你在干嘛。。。我觉得特别的没教养，我在干嘛关你屁事哦", "image": null, "praise_count": 67, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 978044}, {"id": 197122, "content": "只在心里。从不曾说。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 995519}, {"id": 197378, "content": "一个人在喜欢的地方，做喜欢的事", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1016513}, {"id": 197635, "content": "单身", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 933875}, {"id": 196868, "content": "厕所", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1015410}, {"id": 197124, "content": "手机", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 874658}, {"id": 196869, "content": "想独自呆着时没人打扰", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1015403}, {"id": 197125, "content": "半夜的时候才是我自己的，有两小时留给自己想做什么做什么。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 897598}, {"id": 196870, "content": "周围没有人或都是陌生人，安安静静不打扰到自己", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1015416}, {"id": 197638, "content": "宅。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1012379}, {"id": 200454, "content": "隐私", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1004783}, {"id": 196871, "content": "一般应该指思想的空间，思绪不受到别人打扰。当然也会指实体的空间，自己位置的所属权不会被人占用。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1015411}, {"id": 197127, "content": "可以独自思考的空间", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1016113}, {"id": 196872, "content": "一辆小车，可以带我去任何地方，享受阳光，也能在下雨天包容我在其中尽情哭泣。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 77060}, {"id": 197128, "content": "手机电脑还有我不想说话不想理任何人的时候别来招惹我", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1016122}, {"id": 197384, "content": "不用带耳塞睡觉", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1016589}, {"id": 196873, "content": "能做自己在人群中想做的想尝试的但却不敢做的事情的空间", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1015422}, {"id": 197129, "content": "各种小号和备忘录", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1016124}, {"id": 199945, "content": "想贝兼的➕V信 2227887341，曰结", "image": "img/option/option/20170503195749A964UuqavcznB2GF.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1022018}, {"id": 209929, "content": "我的微博小号，网易云账号，我的房间，我的手机，我一个人在外面散步想想些有的没的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1048236}, {"id": 197130, "content": "一个人做事的时候没有人打扰", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 852958}, {"id": 201994, "content": "网络时代?只需一部手机?就多一份收入，多一份任性?微信咨询2227887341?每天至少50-300+，上不封顶，半月轻松入2000+?你不比别人差❗️差别就在于你缺少一个有实力的团队和一颗赚钱的心❤️", "image": "img/option/option/20170509081204C15MrYmuliKg0epV.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1027056}, {"id": 196875, "content": "觉得自由的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 930304}, {"id": 197131, "content": "有自己的思想，做自己认为对的事情，不被外物所困扰", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1016135}, {"id": 196876, "content": "一切", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 299939}, {"id": 197132, "content": "卧室", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1016140}, {"id": 201740, "content": "带上耳机", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1026424}, {"id": 196877, "content": "能让我免受大部分外部事物干扰的小房间，一件沙发 一扇窗 一台小空调足以。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 770560}, {"id": 198669, "content": "不需要适应别人的生活。", "image": "img/option/option/20170501131133k3zdPcUbftGqoDO8", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1015779}, {"id": 196878, "content": "我抽烟我喝酒我听歌我刷剧我洗澡我抠脚\n都别来打扰我???", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 262113}, {"id": 197390, "content": "孤独", "image": "img/option/option/20170427163824hziZHkJu4WC180Xj.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 942374}, {"id": 196879, "content": "我的空间就是在听音乐的时候，没人打扰\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1014045}, {"id": 197647, "content": "单身汪表示 回家就进入了私人空间", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1017153}, {"id": 196880, "content": "日记本", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 612940}, {"id": 197392, "content": "真心", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 197345}, {"id": 202256, "content": "别人没事就盯着你看", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 953681}, {"id": 206864, "content": "演说家", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 908163}, {"id": 196881, "content": "我觉得，对于与我们自己关系近疏不同的人，个人空间的大小是不同的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 678053}, {"id": 198161, "content": "自己在房间里放音乐嗨的时候我妈不合时宜的进来了?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 699035}, {"id": 198417, "content": "不受打扰的做想做的事", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 548420}, {"id": 196882, "content": "可以安心思考、冥想、大声唱歌、走路、跳舞，做什么都没人知道，没人打扰", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 395242}]}